{"title":"“好邻居”","authors":["天马"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":1,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"“好邻居”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们是邻居，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"相处在一起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲密一家人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何分我和你！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的是我的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要我自取，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"物资和金钱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河山和土地……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在你家里面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任我来和去；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你家即我家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不必太介意！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"代你把家管，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这个我乐意，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能者应多劳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不管过不去！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何必谈主权，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"权属我和你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"既然是一家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谈这不亲密。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的是我的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"慷慨我赐你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"样样是宝贝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"价值贵无比。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赐你铁锁链，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"精致世间稀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戴在颈项上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"响声多有趣！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赐你“贫穷丸”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国特制的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一服就有效，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"包你贫如洗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赐你美国货，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"川流水不息，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虽说价钱高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"货色数第一！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还派“和平队”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"常来走亲戚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"感情要交流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文化要统一。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还派美国兵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驻扎你家里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"个个经训练，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杀人好手艺！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱是好邻居，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"声名传万里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"非是我自夸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真是了不起！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天马诗  江有生画（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}